				</a>
				<a href="/auth/google" class="google-btn">
					<img src="/auth/images/btn_google_dark_focus_ios.svg" />
					<p>Login with Google</p>
				</a>
			</div>
			<a href="/" class="return">...or return to the homepage</a>
		</div>
		<div class="divide"></div>
		<div class="col-right">
			<h3>Why do you guys need my facebook/google info?</h3><br/>
			<p>ACM hack will not have access to any of your privately accessible data; we just need a method of keeping track of HackSchool students.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
